{
  "texts": [
    "RNA extracted from tissue following salicylic acid treatment were collected and processed as previously described [40].",
    "Individual and pooled RNA integrity was assessed on an Agilent 2100 Bioanalyzer System.",
    "Illumina TruSeq libraries (150 nt) were prepared using RNA pools at The Pennsylvania State University Huck Institutes of the Life Sciences Genomics Core Facility.",
    "Libraries were then sequenced on an Illumina NextSeq 550 in high output mode at the same facility.Raw RNA-Seq reads were trimmed to remove lowquality bases as well as embedded adaptor sequences and filtered to discard short-read fragments using Trimmomatic v0.33 [56].",
    "We then used FastQC v0.10.1 (https:// www. bioin forma tics."
  ]
}